{
  id: 'prompt-13',
  prompt: 'Research and understand your specific insurance policy coverage, deductibles, and limitations for disaster-related claims',
  category: 'research',
  helpText: 'Understanding your insurance policy details is fundamental to setting realistic expectations and maximizing your claim settlement. Review your homeowner\'s, renter\'s, or business insurance policy to identify what types of damage are covered, what your deductible amounts are, and any specific exclusions or limitations that apply to your situation. Pay special attention to coverage limits for personal property, additional living expenses, and whether you have replacement cost or actual cash value coverage, as these details will significantly impact your settlement amount and recovery planning.'
}
```

This prompt fits the "Foundation and Understanding" theme perfectly as it focuses on understanding the fundamental aspects of insurance coverage that will guide the entire recovery process.

