    helpText: 'Establishing secure document and data backup systems is crucial for protecting irreplaceable items and ensuring quick access to critical information during future emergencies. Scan all important documents (insurance policies, identification, financial records, medical records) to cloud storage, create physical copies stored in multiple secure locations, and establish automated backup systems for digital photos and files. This proactive step prevents the devastating loss of family memories and critical documents that often compounds disaster recovery challenges and ensures you can quickly prove ownership, identity, and financial status if future disasters strike.'
